  "prompt": "Which IIT has best Hostel Rooms?",
  "response": "Determining which Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) has the best hostel rooms can be subjective, as it depends on individual preferences and priorities. However, some IITs are often praised for their hostel facilities:\n\n1. **IIT Bombay**:\n   - Known for its modern infrastructure and well-maintained hostels.\n   - Hostels are equipped with amenities like Wi-Fi, common rooms, and recreational facilities.\n\n2. **IIT Delhi**:\n   - Offers a variety of hostel types, including single rooms, double rooms, and air-conditioned rooms.\n   - Known for its good maintenance and proximity to academic areas.\n\n3. **IIT Madras**:\n   - Known for its spacious rooms and good facilities.\n   - Hostels often have common areas for socializing and studying.\n\n4. **IIT Kharagpur**:\n   - One of the largest hostel systems among IITs.\n   - Known for its green campus and efforts to maintain a comfortable living environment.\n\n5. **IIT Kanpur**:\n   - Offers well-maintained hostels with modern amenities.\n   - Known for its student-friendly environment and good food quality in messes.\n\nEach IIT has its own strengths, and what might be considered \"best\" can vary based on individual needs and preferences. It's recommended to visit the official websites of these institutes or connect with current students to get a more detailed and updated view of the hostel facilities.",
